title: Room For Toys! Ocean View 16258 Chapman Ln., Brookings
text:
Room For Toys! Ocean View 16258 Chapman Ln., Brookings ad date: 10/17/2015 
Ocean View 16258 Chapman Ln., Brookings Need garages? Here you have it with 3 car garages, 1 RV garage and room for more. Set amidst cedar and Douglas fir trees, this 3BD/2BA home on 0.40 acres features a spacious living room, kitchen with a view and dining room. Master suite with ocean view plus a slider to the deck. Covered patio and fenced garden area. No. 15585240 $299,900 Sarah Pettinger
